body_html:
VLOG is always output as INFO log level, so I think VLOG's level (1, 2 ...) is different from LOG's level (info, warning, errors, fatal).
And there is highest level VLOG that is not important compared to the lower level.
Therefore, it is useful to limit output log level from VLOG.
